	<presentation id="index">
		<title>The Why/What/How Maneuver: From Start to Scale</title>
		<toc class="abstract">In this presentation we look at how to move a discussion from talking about individual and isolated technical problems, to understanding and addressing the big picture. This can help when conversations seem to be stuck at discussing technical details, and when the goal is to move the conversation forward to be about the actual business goals. We're looking at some conversational strategies and at typical responses during these conversations. The main goal of this maneuver is to re-frame the initial discussion in a way that better addresses the underlying business goals and that has the ability to scale.</toc>
